You guys probably get this all the time (and you probably won't see this comment), but here's some suggestions for future rap battles:
-Carole King vs. Billy Joel (both are piano-playing New Yorker singer-songwriters who are best known for the music they put out in the 1970s)
-Elton John vs. David Bowie (both are flamboyant rock star icons)
-Billie Joe Armstrong vs. Laura Jane Grace (both are lead singers of punk rock bands with a cult following--and both have three names!)
-Luke Skywalker, Leia Organa, and Han Solo vs. Harry Potter, Ron Weasley, and Hermione Granger (for obvious reasons)
-Scooby and Shaggy vs. Dipper and Mabel (both are mystery-solving duos who no one takes seriously...at first)


Again, I know you guys are super busy, but I'm a diehard fan of the show and I want to contribute to it in any way I can. Love from New Jersey ❤️
